{"tid":1128331,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾意玩Zelda/惡魔城必玩既games~~~~~~~~","createTime":"2019-04-27T17:56:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T06:39:44.000Z","uid":74970,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"53ea3fba70134743113bc882bd68dc8ecadd7c26","tid":1128331,"uid":74970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:56:57.000Z","msg":"hollow knight, dead cells, salt &amp; sanctuary果d出名正既就唔講啦<br />\n講d我覺得正又少人玩既驚<br />\n<br />\n1.CrossCode<br />\n有好多zelda式解謎, 同時有流暢刺激既戰鬥, <br />\n系統豐富, 玩法多, 幾十粒鐘無悶場<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MwcLQzgp7Bk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMwcLQzgp7Bk&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8msgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=887294d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MwcLQzgp7Bk</a><br />\n<br />\n2.supraland<br />\n新出既沙盒驚, 混合左zelda/惡魔城/portal果種玩法, 解謎搵方法過關幾考智力<br />\n探索地圖都好好玩, 周圍都係隱藏地方同謎題, 畫風得意<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qFsXKSAHhVU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqFsXKSAHhVU&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8msgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=4b516500\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qFsXKSAHhVU</a><br />\n<br />\n3.Death gambit<br />\n惡魔城+dark souls, 去類似hollow knight同salt &amp; sanctuary, <br />\n以取捨攻擊定血量黎豪睹, 去挑戰敵人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0OacwTFrww8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0OacwTFrww8&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8msgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=bb8a4460\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0OacwTFrww8</a>"},{"pid":"5b3cd029e92fa328a2658f25152dcf8c9aca508f","tid":1128331,"uid":74970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T18:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264f0d4142b9435220f849d007976765a0ed45d6","tid":1128331,"uid":128830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply